sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor A as Admin
    participant X as REXPrimary<br/>(Sepolia)
    participant K as Keeper
    participant H as Hyperlane<br/>Bridge
    participant E as PruvExecutor<br/>(PRUV)
    participant P as Pruv RWAToken
    actor R as Retail

    A->>X: triggerWindDown()
    X->>X: khoá subscription mới
    X->>X: refund toàn bộ sub pending
    Note over X,R: retail đã tự cầm wRWA của mình (no custody)

    X->>H: bridge wRWA trong redeem-queue sang PRUV
    H-->>E: giao wRWA
    E->>P: redeem
    P-->>E: USDC
    E->>H: bridge USDC về
    H-->>X: giao USDC
    K->>X: settle - phân phối USDC cho redeem-queue
    R->>X: claim(receipt)
    X-->>R: USDC
    Note over X: 🔒 có ép redeem hộ wRWA retail đang cầm không? (chờ David, T2.4)
    Note over X: đóng (Closed)
